"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/693385","Department for Transport","false","2017-03-02","<p>a) The companies that have been awarded contracts since 2010 with HS2 Ltd can be found in Annex A.</p><p>b) The information requested is not held centrally and could only be obtained at disproportionate cost.</p>","South Holland and The Deepings","Mr John Hayes",,"2017-03-02T16:03:34.49Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/693385/answer","Biography information for Sir John Hayes","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/693385/answer","065186 - Annex A - List of HS2Ltd contracts.docx","065186 - Annex A  - List of contracts with HS2 Ltd","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/693385/answer",,,,,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2017-02-22","High Speed Two","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, if he will list all the companies which have been awarded contracts with (a) HS2 Ltd and (b) his Department in each year since 2010.","false","Biography information for Antoinette Sandbach","Eddisbury","Antoinette Sandbach","65186"
